#!name=Sinopec去广告
#!desc=针对Sinopec广告进行拦截，要重新安装清除缓存拦截广告才会生效！
#!author=Serein1202[https://github.com/Serein1202]
#!icon=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Serein1202/Loon/refs/heads/main/test/Sinopec/Sinopec.png
